flowchart TD
    A[SendMessageProcessor.processRequest] --> B[sendMessage]
    B --> C{事务预备消息?}
    C -- 是 --> D[TransactionalMessageService.asyncPrepareMessage]
    C -- 否 --> E[MessageStore.asyncPutMessage]
    E --> F[DefaultMessageStore.asyncPutMessage]
    F --> G[CommitLog.asyncPutMessage]
    G --> H[编码消息]
    H --> I[获取 TopicQueueLock / PutMessageLock]
    I --> J[MappedFileQueue.getLastMappedFile]
    J --> K[MappedFile.appendMessage]
    K --> L[AppendMessageCallback]
    L --> M[handleDiskFlushAndHA]
    M --> N[返回 PutMessageResult]
